  "noisy_sentences": "<noisy_sentences>The restaurant has been serving the same menu for as long as anyone can remember.; I'm really looking forward to trying out the new restaurant that just opened up downtown.; discovery; 876; 878; I'm really looking forward to trying the new vegan ice cream shop that just opened down the street.</noisy_sentences>",
  "denoised_question": "<denoised_question>I have five different pairs of socks. Each day (for five days) I pick two socks at random without replacement to wear for the day. Find the probability that I wear matching socks on both the third day and the fifth day.</denoised_question>",
